## Azure-Backed Behavior

`display_name` renames the Azure subscription through the Azure Management API. `azure_owner_object_id` creates an Azure `Owner` role assignment on the created subscription for the configured Azure principal object ID. Changing either field only calls the Azure Management API and does not modify the Marketplace subscription document.

See [Troubleshooting](../guides/troubleshooting.md) for common Marketplace user lookup and Azure preflight errors.
